<p class="body-text">We never use calendered (cheap) vinyl. Cast vinyl conforms to curves without shrinking, cracking, or peeling — critical for Chicago's extreme temperature swings from -10°F winters to 95°F+ summers. If another shop is quoting you 40% less, ask what vinyl they use.</p>
